00:38:09,160 --> 00:38:12,311
That little tree is in trouble.
Come on.

523
00:38:12,400 --> 00:38:15,039
Look at it. Oh!

524
00:38:15,120 --> 00:38:18,157
It's suffocating. It's the smog.

525
00:38:18,240 --> 00:38:21,835
