is not really a human trait.

550
00:39:53,920 --> 00:39:55,956
What is that up there?

551
00:39:56,040 --> 00:39:57,871
Oh, that's my umbrella.

552
00:39:57,960 --> 00:40:01,873
That's just a relic. I found it when
I was packing to come to America.

553
00:40:01,960 --> 00:40:05,270
It used to be my defence
on picket lines and rallies

554
00:40:05,360 --> 00:40:07,112
and political meetings,

555
00:40:07,200 --> 00:40:10,988
being dragged off by the police
and attacked by thugs.

556
00:40:11,080 --> 00:40:12,911
What were you fighting for?

557
00:40:14,000 --> 00:40:17,709
Oh, big issue.
Liberty, rights, justice.

558
00:40:17,800 --> 00:40:21,110
Kings died, kingdoms fell.

559
00:40:21,200 --> 00:40:23,395
I don't regret the kingdom.

560
00:40:23,480 --> 00:40:28,270
What sense in borders
and nations and patriotism?

561
00:40:30,320 --> 00:40:32,470
But I miss the kings.

562
00:40:33,920 --> 00:40:37,993
When I was a little girl,
I was taken to the palace in Vienna

563
00:40:38,080 --> 00:40:39,638
to a garden party.

564
00:40:39,720 --> 00:40:44,316
I can still see the sun shining,
the parasols,

565
00:40:44,400 --> 00:40:47,472
the flashing uniforms
of the young officers.

566
00:40:47,560 --> 00:40:50,472
I thought then
that I would marry a soldier.

567
00:40:52,720 --> 00:40:55,473
Later on,
Frederick would chide me about it.

568
00:40:57,240 --> 00:40:59,674
He was so serious.

569
00:41:01,600 --> 00:41:04,353
A doctor at the university...

570
00:41:04,440 --> 00:41:06,192
and in the government.

571
00:41:18,360 --> 00:41:21,033
But that was all before.

572
00:41:30,560 --> 00:41:32,118
So...

573
00:41:35,480 --> 00:41:37,675
you don't use the umbrella any more?

574
00:41:41,880 --> 00:41:43,757
No more revolts?

575
00:41:47,320 --> 00:41:49,390
Oh, oh, yes.

576
00:41:49,480 --> 00:41:52,233
Oh! Every day...

577
00:41:52,320 --> 00:41:57,838
but... I don't need a defence
any more, I embrace.

578
00:41:57,920 --> 00:42:00,514
Still fighting for the big issues

579
00:42:00,600 --> 00:42:04,229
but now in my small, individual way.

