- I don't play anything.
- Nothing?!

615
00:44:06,360 --> 00:44:09,955
Dear me! Everybody should be able
to make some music.

616
00:44:10,040 --> 00:44:13,032
That's the cosmic dance.
Oh, come with me.

617
00:44:13,120 --> 00:44:15,429
