649
00:47:03,680 --> 00:47:06,035
Er, oh, no, I just took it.

650
00:47:06,120 --> 00:47:09,556
- You took it?
- Yes, I have to plant my tree.

651
00:47:09,640 --> 00:47:12,359
Well, it's not mine really

652
00:47:12,440 --> 00:47:16,513
but we would like to get it
into soil as soon as possible.

653
00:47:18,040 --> 00:47:20,031
